    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hi, you can set the [`future.persistHierarchicalRootCount`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/instantsearch/js/#widget-param-persisthierarchicalrootcount) in your InstantSearch widget to prevent refinements from updating the count dispayed at the refined root level.",
